 LP22 is built for roles that require holding a large-scale vision while staying grounded in practical steps. Organizational leadership, architecture, global nonprofit work, social entrepreneurship, institutional transformation, scientific research with world-changing implications. These are domains where LP22 finds the scope their nature requires.
